{"word":"G987 - βλασφημέω - blasphēméō - blas-fay-meh'-o - Blaspheme","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βλασφημέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>blasphēméō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>blas-fay-meh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Blaspheme"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தூஷி, இகழு, தேவதூஷணம் சொல்லு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to speak reproachfully, rail at, revile, calumniate"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G989 - βλάσφημος - blásphēmos - blas'-fay-mos/989\">G989</a>; to <i>vilify</i>; specifically to <i>speak impiously:</i> - (speak) blaspheme (-er, -mously, -my), defame, rail on, revile, speak evil."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G987 - βλασφημέω - blasphēméō - blas-fay-meh'-o/987\">G987</a>, <a href=\"#/G988 - βλασφημία - blasphēmía - blas-fay-me'-ah/988\">G988</a>, <a href=\"#/G989 - βλάσφημος - blásphēmos - blas'-fay-mos/989\">G989</a>"}]}